{
    "content": "<div style='display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;'><img src='../img/server.png' alt='zeek' style='width: 100px; height: 100px;'></div> <div style='padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;'><font color='teal'><h3>Zeek</h3></font></div>",
    "depth": 1,
    "children": [
        {
            "content": "<h4>开源的网络流量分析工具</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "区别于传统防火墙、IDS、IPS, Zeek 更聚焦在为用户提供对网络流量的获取、表达及分析的能力上",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "将获取到的网络流量转化成格式化的文本, 即 Zeek 日志",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "提供一套具有图灵完备性的编程语言—— Zeek 脚本",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "主要提供对 OSI 中网络层至应用层协议的流量分析能力",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "4.0 即之后的版本新增了包分析框架, 从而使得 Zeek 具有了分析数据链路层数据帧的能力",
                            "depth": 3
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "但相关的内置分析脚本还不丰富, 分析手段也较为简单",
                            "depth": 3
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "<h4>部署使用</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "基于标准 libpcap 接口获取流量包",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "核心代码: C++",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "仅支持在类 UNIX 操作系统中（包括 Linux、FreeBSD 及 macOS）运行",
                    "depth": 3
                },
                {
                    "content": "支持单点部署及集群式部署, 并提供配套的集群管理工具 ZeekControl",
                    "depth": 3
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "command",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "<code><b>Zeek</b></code>",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-a|--parse-only</code> 脚本解析后直接退出",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-b|--bare-mode</code> 不载入内置的协议分析脚本",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-e|--exec <zeek code></code> 执行脚本 e.g. 'print \"Hello World!\";'",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-f|--filter <filter> 过滤规则 e.g. 'port 80'</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-i|--iface <interface></code> 网络接口",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-p|--prefix <prefix></code> 同时加载前缀为 prefix. 的文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-r|--readfile <readfile></code> 读取 pcap 文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-s|--rulefile <rulefile></code> 特征文件(signature, .sig 文件)",
                            "depth": 4,
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<code>e.g.<br>signature test-signature {<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;ip-proto == tcp<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;dst-port = 80<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;payload .*passwd/ <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;event \"payload of dst-port=80/tcp contains 'passwd'\"<br>}</code>",
                                    "depth": 5
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-v|--version</code> 版本号",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-w|--writefile <writefile></code> 分析流量的同时将流量数据包写入文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-C|--no-checksums</code> 关闭对数据包校验和的检查",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-D|--deterministic</code> 关闭随时生成 uid 的功能",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-G|--load-seeds <file></code> 载入随机数种子文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-H|--save-seeds <file></code> 保存随机数种子文件",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-I|--print-id <ID name></code> 某个脚本变量的类型定义",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-N|--print-plugins</code> 已加载的插件信息",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code>-X|--zeekygen</code> 生成 Zeek 脚本相关注释",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "content": "<code><b>zeekctl</b></code>",
                    "depth": 3
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "<h4>发现网络资产</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
            "children": [
                {
                    "content": "script",
                    "depth": 3,
                    "children": [
                        {
                            "content": "<code><PREFIX>/share/zeek/policy/protocols/conn/known-hosts.zeek</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "<code><PREFIX>/share/zeek/policy/protocols/conn/known-services.zeek</code>",
                            "depth": 4
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": "<h4>网络扫描</h4>",
            "depth": 2,
